Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.85,0:00:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你們  按我說的動動手看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.62,0:00:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是殺害賽門·漢特的機關
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.34,0:00:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是稱為「活結」的綁法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.96,0:00:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解開繩結的魔術裡經常使用
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.31,0:00:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修女摩瑞拉就是這樣解開繩子  拿到短劍的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.44,0:00:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的嗎  小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.67,0:00:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  這根本算不上混沌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.78,0:00:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真正想重新拼湊的是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.22,0:00:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.24,0:00:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.05,0:00:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  啊嚏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.35,0:00:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.44,0:01:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝剛才幫了我們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.97,0:01:04.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像來的時候也是一起的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.72,0:01:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  有空位哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.03,0:01:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不  那個我…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.29,0:01:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.58,0:01:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  能一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.66,0:02:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了啊  其他地方全都是滿員啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.60,0:03:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問…兩位是什麼關係？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.72,0:03:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有座位在迷惘的時候  這位先生就在走廊上叫我了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.96,0:03:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  來自我介紹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.35,0:03:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣坐一起也是一種緣分
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.03,0:03:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐  你為什麼會去那種修道院
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.80,0:03:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是孤兒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.70,0:03:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道自己的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.08,0:03:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那樣死後去黃泉國的時候會迷路的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.24,0:03:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就想要找到它  就參加魔術幻燈秀之夜了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.82,0:03:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  阿姨你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.78,0:03:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我就是稻草人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.84,0:03:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平常在偏遠鄉下的農場裡  監視著壞小鳥們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.47,0:03:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問  這是什麼遊戲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.56,0:03:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意思  那我就算是騎士了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.20,0:03:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騎著愛馬在荒野上奔馳  把壞人一個個全部砍倒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.59,0:03:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.23,0:04:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樵夫就好了  我做不了那麼勇猛的事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.76,0:04:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最多就只能砍砍樹了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.27,0:04:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是膽小的少爺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.00,0:04:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  你們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.05,0:04:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.99,0:04:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高貴太古灰狼和其糊塗僕人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.90,0:04:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  我絕對不是糊塗…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.71,0:04:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.47,0:04:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx70\fscy70\pos(457,647)}Masquerade
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.47,0:04:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假面舞會號這名字起得真是妙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.50,0:04:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是如假面舞會一般
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.12,0:04:34.13,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(645,560)}漆黑的列車運送著幾個謊言
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.30,0:04:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的相信嗎  幼狼能把那個盒子奪回來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.75,0:04:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個對我們灰狼來說就是王牌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.95,0:04:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能從迫近的暴風雨中保護那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.54,0:04:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就托付給她了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.12,0:04:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我們要怎麼辦  難得都跑到這裡來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.97,0:05:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心  辦法其它還有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.83,0:05:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女兒啊  解開謎團  然後為了活下去而展示力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.34,0:05:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失蹤的雷格蘭千金至今行蹤不明
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.25,0:05:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘇瓦爾發生這種案件了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.40,0:05:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  維多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.06,0:05:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來剛才有什麼想說的  是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.70,0:05:24.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城  遺物箱是什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.73,0:05:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有相關的知識嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.48,0:05:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.07,0:05:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺物箱就是  一部分歐洲地區流傳的習慣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.37,0:05:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小的箱子裡  放滿了各種表現人生章節的物品
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.65,0:05:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人死了之後箱子會和棺材一起埋葬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.66,0:05:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是人生的象徵之類的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.27,0:05:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.10,0:05:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在別西卜的頭骨裡的那個箱子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.31,0:05:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕也封印著某人的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.17,0:05:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後媽媽她們想要得到那個箱子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.64,0:06:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺物箱  必須要查明它的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.56,0:06:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇了我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.14,0:06:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.68,0:06:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好重
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.60,0:06:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.12,0:06:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  給我記著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.67,0:06:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們  全身濕著的話會感冒的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.86,0:06:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去和乘務員說  借點什麼穿的來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.76,0:06:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.54,0:06:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.83,0:06:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.27,0:06:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  騎士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.07,0:06:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吹夜風吹的有點冷了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.27,0:06:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能讓阿姨也幫我拿一份來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.58,0:06:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.02,0:06:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.59,0:06:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少爺就在這等著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.93,0:07:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實現公主願望的是  騎士的義務
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.93,0:07:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.70,0:07:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來幽會的嗎  在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.92,0:07:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丟棄稻草人的職責  對別人的收穫出手真是不規矩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.55,0:07:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從我夥伴那裡拿來的東西  還給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.72,0:07:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.86,0:07:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真慢啊  他們兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.78,0:07:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  剛才聽到了不該聽的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.68,0:07:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.11,0:08:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日  能找到就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.18,0:08:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛  剛才外面有人…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.18,0:08:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.18,0:08:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.91,0:08:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給  替換的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.27,0:08:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問…稻草人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.25,0:08:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好遇見熟人  好像換房間了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.76,0:08:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很開心的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.39,0:08:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.59,0:08:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去換衣服了  久城
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.55,0:08:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到的確實不是幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.94,0:08:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知生死  但是已經有人從這舞台上退場了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.17,0:08:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.13,0:08:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說剛才的是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.95,0:08:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是自稱稻草人的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.43,0:09:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個房間裡面的所有人  不是靈異部就是學院的手下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.30,0:09:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來混進不得了的假面舞會了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.09,0:09:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是已經想好辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.15,0:09:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這舞蹈的中心裡的應該就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.41,0:09:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是要如此斷言混沌的碎片還不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.69,0:09:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.76,0:09:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  因為太合身了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.31,0:09:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然說合身  想讓我伺候你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.35,0:09:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變得了不起了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.26,0:09:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明沒有這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.31,0:09:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.96,0:09:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.65,0:09:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著我  我一定會…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.26,0:09:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.29,0:09:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無線？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.12,0:10:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樵夫  在和誰通話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.38,0:10:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.13,0:10:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？  都在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.59,0:10:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為太慢  就來找你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.64,0:10:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.78,0:10:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  樵夫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.86,0:10:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去餐車嗎  一直喝到天亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.36,0:10:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯啊  不過得是你請客
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.52,0:10:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.82,0:10:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能招待我們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.60,0:10:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.20,0:10:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  伏特加
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.60,0:11:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取葡萄乾遊戲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.14,0:11:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把火裡的葡萄快速取出來吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.20,0:11:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後說出自己願望的遊戲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.14,0:11:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道的真清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.94,0:11:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  誰先來拿這個葡萄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.52,0:11:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  可以的話我來…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.13,0:11:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我先來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.28,0:11:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明年也想看到故鄉的春天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.44,0:11:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為喜歡鳶尾那美麗的花朵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.09,0:11:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.46,0:11:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.74,0:11:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為了這個的話  要背叛同伴的樵夫們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.97,0:11:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那接下來就是我了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.70,0:12:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這葡萄吃了不會中毒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.14,0:12:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.72,0:12:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.11,0:12:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝點水會比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.77,0:12:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用你多事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.63,0:12:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是說願望來著？  這個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.29,0:12:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.45,0:12:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.23,0:12:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也希望你能平安回到故鄉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.05,0:12:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此話怎講
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.83,0:12:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如說…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.83,0:12:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  別喝那水！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.13,0:12:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.70,0:12:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別演戲了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.21,0:12:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你下的毒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.68,0:12:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.56,0:13:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在場的有醫生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.38,0:13:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說我下毒？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.60,0:13:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別胡說  你也看見了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.53,0:13:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也吃了同一盆的葡萄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.60,0:13:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水我也喝了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.25,0:13:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毒是下在杯底  凍得薄薄的一層
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.63,0:13:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和她最初喝的時候  毒還沒溶解在水中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.21,0:13:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而就當冰開始融化  她再次喝的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.04,0:13:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.41,0:13:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  你不適合手槍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.70,0:13:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷格蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.72,0:13:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你會知道我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.31,0:13:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我  這荒唐假面舞會所圍繞的中心是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.06,0:14:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡的靈異部
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.30,0:14:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這盒子我死也不會給你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.77,0:14:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盒子？  那果然是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.51,0:14:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  太勉強了  這樣亂動的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.12,0:14:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了  反正這列車上的所有人都會死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.79,0:14:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的定時聯絡一旦中斷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.44,0:14:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同夥就會讓這列車脫軌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.36,0:14:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其讓靈異部奪走那個  不如毀掉整輛列車
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.54,0:14:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們就給我待在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.74,0:14:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去控制室  讓火車停下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.46,0:15:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.89,0:15:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.89,0:15:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利加  就在那等我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.80,0:15:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然也我要去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.72,0:15:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.57,0:15:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.63,0:15:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走吧  抓緊我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.43,0:15:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.61,0:15:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別想走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.82,0:15:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.14,0:15:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.31,0:16:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來騎士意外落馬了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.75,0:16:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作一點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.06,0:16:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別…碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.78,0:16:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盒子…誰也…絕對
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.85,0:16:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種東西無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.60,0:16:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的性命才更重要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.00,0:16:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鐵橋…裡面…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.41,0:16:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.67,0:16:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好害怕  我想知道生日…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.74,0:17:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.13,0:17:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這距離還是太遠了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.55,0:17:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.55,0:17:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看那個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.78,0:17:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.02,0:17:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是引爆裝置吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.01,0:17:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓這列車脫軌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.55,0:17:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.39,0:17:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,子彈只剩下一發
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.37,0:17:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我  下次一定打中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.99,0:17:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那不可能  還是我來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.12,0:17:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽說過  為了活下去而展現自己的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.79,0:17:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要親手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.89,0:18:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了  但是我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.44,0:18:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  讓你幫我一把
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.08,0:18:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人和僕人要齊心協力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.06,0:18:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.78,0:18:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城  對於灰狼來說沒有任何不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.68,0:18:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.41,0:18:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經驗什麼的不過是愚蠢的野蠻人的胡話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.87,0:18:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我沒開過槍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.62,0:18:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我卻熟悉它的原理
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.19,0:18:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題  你一定做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.41,0:18:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡過這場風暴  我們倆一起回去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.31,0:18:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到我們的聖瑪格麗特學園
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.87,0:18:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.98,0:18:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是現在！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.11,0:19:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.37,0:19:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧  我做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.03,0:19:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  你做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.58,0:19:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  接下來該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.90,0:19:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.21,0:19:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒煤了  遲早會自己停下來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.04,0:19:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失蹤的雷格蘭小姐的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.61,0:19:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是你的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.65,0:19:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靈異部綁架了你的妹妹作為人質
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.52,0:20:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了能利用你當臨時間諜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.04,0:20:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不惜如此他們也想得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.22,0:20:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個遺物箱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.97,0:20:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面有描述某個男人一生的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.91,0:20:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出生了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.11,0:20:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是從盒子主人的身上切下來的臍帶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.86,0:20:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成長了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.22,0:20:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是他的肖像畫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.27,0:20:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.51,0:20:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意中人的香水瓶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.98,0:20:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨後他遇到了挫折
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.73,0:20:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「絕不回頭」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.68,0:20:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只寫了一句話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.70,0:20:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面就只有這些了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.80,0:20:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而這遺物箱還沒結束
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.75,0:20:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說這盒子的主人還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.27,0:20:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.06,0:20:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這盒子不是在墳墓中而是藏在某人家的地板下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.77,0:21:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那無名村  藏著我媽媽照片的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.80,0:21:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說  盒子的主人和柯蒂麗亞女士一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.71,0:21:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他之名為
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.33,0:21:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丘比特·羅傑  七歲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.76,0:21:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在塞倫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.56,0:21:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.92,0:21:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科學院領導人  丘比特·羅傑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.76,0:21:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏偏是有濃厚風俗的無名村出身的灰狼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.20,0:21:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是足以撼動政治力量的平衡的重大事實
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.90,0:21:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此  靈異部…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.76,0:21:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想奪取這箱子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.04,0:21:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後科學院拼命也要阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.82,0:21:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我重新拼湊的就這麼多了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.99,0:21:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.58,0:21:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道靈異部會怎麼用它
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.76,0:21:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過有這個箱子的話  你妹妹就能得救了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.30,0:21:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  維多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.66,0:22:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.05,0:22:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.11,0:22:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.53,0:22:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那東西交給布洛瓦侯爵的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.22,0:22:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.92,0:22:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽交給我的謎題我解開了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.61,0:22:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我手上還有王牌
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.84,0:24:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有餡餅  也沒有杏仁餅乾
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.74,0:24:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  有餡餅也有杏仁餅乾哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.56,0:24:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  請用
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.70,0:24:15.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  這是歌詞…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.31,0:24:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.02,0:24:19.02,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(638,550)}薔薇色的人生被埋於新雪之下


